1. Check adding product to the cart.
    1.Click on the Add to cart button on a product.
    2.Click on the Cart button.
2. Check the Remove button on the cart page.
    1.Click on the Remove button.
3. Check the Continue shopping button.
    1.Click on Cart button.
    1.Click on the Continue Shopping button.
4. Check the Checkout page.
    1.Click on the Add to cart button on a product.
    2.Click on the Cart button.
    3.Click on the Checkout button.
5. Check the validation errors on the Checkout page.
    1.Leave empty the First Name field.
    2.Click on the Continue button.
    3.Leave empty the Last Name field.
    4.Click on the Continue button.
    5.Leave empty the Zip code field.
    6.Click on the Continue button.
6. Check the Cancel button on Checkout page.
    1.Click on Cancel button.
7. Check Continue button with correct values.
    1.Click on the Checkout button.
    2.Fill in First name field.
    3.Fill in Last name field.
    4.Fill in Zip code.
    5.Click on the Continue button.
8. Check Cancel button on Overview page.
    1.Click Cancel button on Checkout Overview page.
9.Check the Finishing a purchase
    1.Click the cart button.
    2.Click the Checkout button.
    3.Fill in required fields.
    4.Click the Continue button.
    5.Click the Finish button.
10. Check the Back home button.
    1.Click on the Back home button.

